column5: Anyone know of a mom and pop motel between Duluth and Pigeon River?
try:http://www.whisperingpinesmotel.com/ we'll be there in less than two weeks. phish
Check out Grand Marais. Super 8 is nice and affordable. Stayed at 3 others but forget the names (all nice for an overnight). We have stayed last 2 years at Casino before border.
The OutPost Motel, 5 minutes west of Grand Marais, great view of the lake and affordable. Sturg
